<div class="container main-container main-container--cream container-shadow text-center">   
  <div class="row main-row">
    <div class="col-sm-12 cup__header-col text-center">
      <h1>I gadget di Dora & Miss Tressy</h1>
      <h2><%= @cup_tag.description %></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-12 cup__header-col text-center">
      <div class="row main-row">
        <img class="img-responsive hidden-xs" src="<%= @cup_tag_extra_fields["form_steps"]["url"] rescue nil %>">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cup__submit">
    <%= link_to "RICHIEDI I GADGET", "/gadget/step_1", { :class => "btn btn-red btn-lg btn-xlg" } %>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container main-container text-center">
  <div class="row main-row main-row-centered-elements">
    <div class="col-sm-4">
      <p class="cup__title">Hai acquistato almeno 2 confezioni?</p>
      <p>Richiedi il tuo gadget</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-8">
      <img class="img-responsive cup__select-cup-image" src="<%= @cup_tag_extra_fields["two_cups"]["url"] rescue nil %>">
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container main-container text-center">
  <div class="row main-row">
    <div class="col-sm-4">
      <img class="img-responsive cup__select-cup-image" src="<%= @cup_tag_extra_fields["two_packages_gadget"]["url"] rescue nil %>">
      <p><b> 2 confezioni = 1 tovaglietta </b></p><br/>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-4">
      <img class="img-responsive cup__select-cup-image" src="<%= @cup_tag_extra_fields["three_packages_gadget"]["url"] rescue nil %>">
      <p><b> 3 confezioni = 1 tovaglietta + 1 tazza oppure 2 tovagliette </b></p><br/>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-4">
      <img class="img-responsive cup__select-cup-image" src="<%= @cup_tag_extra_fields["five_packages_gadget"]["url"] rescue nil %>">
      <p><b> 2 confezioni = 2 tovagliette e 2 tazze </b></p><br/>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row main-row">
    <% for i in 1..3 %>
      <div class="col-sm-4">
        <%= link_to "RICHIEDI", "/gadget/step_1", { :class => "btn btn-red btn-md" } %>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container main-container text-center">
  <div class="row main-row">
    <p class="cup__footer">
      I prodotti Orzoro che partecipano alla promozione sono Orzoro Classico, Orzoro Ecco, Orzoro e Cacao, Orzoro e Caff√®.
      Puoi acquistare questi prodotti con le combinazioni che preferisci.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>